    "lineId": "l-0006",
    "blockId": "b-002",
    "mode": "explain",
    "lang": "en",
    "text": "By the end of this video, you won't need to point. You'll order in Thai, ask for recommendations, tell them how spicy you want it, and get the bill — all in Thai.",
